    <header>
                <p class="tag"><a
                    href="https://reason.com/tag/coronavirus/">Coronavirus</a></p>        <h1 class="entry-title">The Post-Pandemic 'New Normal' Looks Awfully Authoritarian</h1>
        
                    <h2 class="entry-subtitle">Less-intrusive responses could preserve our health while leaving our freedom intact. </h2>
                <p class="meta">
            <span class="byline author vcard">
        <a href="https://reason.com/people/jd-tuccille/" title="Posts by J.D. Tuccille" class="author url fn" rel="author">J.D. Tuccille</a>
         </span>
    
    
                                <span class="pipe">|</span>
                <time class="updated" datetime="2020-10-05T10:00:43-04:00">10.5.2020 10:00 AM</time>
                </p>                    <div class="rcom-social-tools"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2Fthe-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--facebook" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Facebook" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2Fthe-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian%2F&text=The+%E2%80%9Cnew+normal%E2%80%9D+of+life+after+COVID-19+threatens+to+look+a+lot+like+old-fashioned+authoritarianism%2C+warns+%40JD_Tuccille&via=reason" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--twitter" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Twitter" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2Fthe-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian%2F&title=The+%E2%80%9Cnew+normal%E2%80%9D+of+life+after+COVID-19+threatens+to+look+a+lot+like+old-fashioned+authoritarianism%2C+warns+%40JD_Tuccille" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--reddit" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Reddit" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-reddit"></i></a><a href="mailto:?subject=Shared+From+Reason.com%3A+The+%E2%80%9Cnew+normal%E2%80%9D+of+life+after+COVID-19+threatens+to+look+a+lot+like+old-fashioned+authoritarianism%2C+warns+%40JD_Tuccille&body=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2Fthe-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--email" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Email" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a><a href="https://reason.com/2020/10/05/the-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian/printer/" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--print" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Print" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fas fa-print"></i></a><span data-link="https://reason.com/2020/10/05/the-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian/" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--copy-link" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Copyurl" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></span><div class="media-links"><a href="/media-contact/" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Media Contact Link Clicked" data-ga-action="Media Contact Link Clicked" data-ga-label="article header">Media Contact &amp; Reprint Requests</a></div></div>
                            		<div class="featured-image">
					<div class="img-wrap">
							<picture style="max-width: 100%; height: auto">
											<source
							type="image/webp"
							data-lazy-srcset="https://d2eehagpk5cl65.cloudfront.net/img/c2400x1350-w2400-q80/uploads/2020/10/mrpphotos526263-2400x1350.jpg.webp 2400w,https://d2eehagpk5cl65.cloudfront.net/img/c1200x675-w1200-q80/uploads/2020/10/mrpphotos526263-1200x675.jpg.webp 1200w,https://d2eehagpk5cl65.cloudfront.net/img/c800x450-w800-q80/uploads/2020/10/mrpphotos526263-800x450.jpg.webp 800w,https://d2eehagpk5cl65.cloudfront.net/img/c600x338-w600-q80/uploads/2020/10/mrpphotos526263-600x338.jpg.webp 600w,https://d2eehagpk5cl65.cloudfront.net/img/c331x186-w331-q80/uploads/2020/10/mrpphotos526263-331x186.jpg.webp 331w"
