					<cite class="fn"><strong>Jackand Ace</strong></cite>				</div>
				<div>
					<a class="comment-time comment-link"
						href="https://reason.com/2020/10/05/the-post-pandemic-new-normal-looks-awfully-authoritarian/#comment-8501355">
						October.5.2020 at 11:06 am					</a>
